edu.rit.pj2.test

Class Test09

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.rit.pj2.Job
      • edu.rit.pj2.test.Test09

  • public class Test09
extends Job
    Class Test09 is a unit test main program for classes Job and Task. The job writes a number of initial tuples into tuple space, each tuple containing a string specified on the command line. Each of these tuples spawns a task that waits 5 seconds, then prints the string on the standard output.

    Usage: java pj2 edu.rit.pj2.test.Test09 string ...
